'''The Birth of the Lightsaber''' was a featurette in the bonus material of [[2004]] DVD release of the ''Star Wars'' [[original trilogy]]. It revealed how the [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] was made, from tape to rotoscoping. It was also included in a DVD that was packaged with select [[Hasbro]] lightsabers alongside two chapters of ''[[Star Wars: Clone Wars]]''.

